  "body": "<img alt=\"5a-20140404-085056.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/718f77877414b43c.jpg?v=1782533476\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"5b-20140404-085108.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/66fb1d22f738c131.jpg?v=1782533479\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5c-20140404-085116.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/e1395e8896e6e237.jpg?v=1782533482\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>So I was just a bit ecstatic about meeting <a href=\"http://lisacongdon.com/\">Lisa Congdon</a> Thursday at the welcome dinner for <a href=\"http://www.craftcationconference.com/\">Craftcation</a>. She delivered a super inspiring visual treat of a keynote speech and slideshow - a delightful balance of honesty, humility, wit and wisdom.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/52e0e9837dcf7305.jpg?v=1782533485\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Bamboo met Lisa at lunch yesterday, and shortly afterwards she decided to curl up next to my signed copy of <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1452124833/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=1452124833&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20\">Whatever You Are, Be A Good One</a>. Here's a lovely page from it which pretty much sums up the whole experience.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/00f00ac473a5d89a.jpg?v=1782533487\"/>\n\n\n</figure>"
}